SUMMARY:The Banff Mountain Film Festival Showing
DESCRIPTION:Rocknasium is excited to host another evening showing of the Banff Mountain Film Festival. The evening will feature showings of multiple award-winning films that explore adventure\, environmental issues\, and action sports. There will be a prize draw during intermission with prizes from Banff international sponsors and local Davis sponsors. Doors open at 6:30pm and films start roughly at 7pm.
