SUMMARY:Make Natural Lip Balm
DESCRIPTION:This hands-on workshop invites you to take a break and have some chemistry fun. You’ll learn about nourishing herbs that can be infused into oils to make luscious lip balms using all natural ingredients. We’ll even pick some from my garden! Working side by side\, we’ll explore basic recipes\, melting and mixing oils and waxes\, and adding subtle scents or colors. \nPut your phone down\, chat\, munch on snacks\, and make something you’ll use every day. Everyone will create several lip balms to take home\, and you’ll have a straightforward recipe if you did want to tackle the mess at home. \n7-9pm. Address will be sent out the week of the workshop.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/make-natural-lip-balm/
LOCATION:Fera House\, Davis\, CA\, 95616
CATEGORIES:Art,Community,Featured,Science
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/IMG_2101.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Fera House":MAILTO:ContactFeraHouse@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
